Node JS (Centos)

https://www.e2enetworks.com/help/knowledge-base/how-to-install-node-js-and-npm-on-centos/

yum install -y gcc-c++ make

curl -sL https://rpm.nodesource.com/setup_6.x | sudo -E bash -

yum install nodejs

check :
node -v 
npm -v 

Folder :
/usr/share/node

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

update node js
https://tecadmin.net/upgrade-nodejs-via-npm/

sudo npm cache clean -f 

sudo npm install -g n 

sudo n stable

sudo ln -sf /usr/local/n/versions/node/11.8.0/bin/node /usr/bin/node

node -v 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

install express generator global

npm install express-generator -g

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

install pm2 

npm install pm2 -g